# Title: UAC Bypass Abusing Winsat Path Parsing - Process
# Author: Christian Burkard (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2021-08-30
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the pattern of UAC Bypass using a path parsing issue in winsat.exe (UACMe 52)
# MITRE Tactic: Privilege Escalation
# Tags: attack.privilege-escalation, attack.t1548.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_uac_bypass_winsat.yml

IntegrityLevel IN ("High", "System", "S-1-16-16384", "S-1-16-12288") ParentCommandLine="*C:\\Windows \\system32\\winsat.exe*" ParentImage="*\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\system32\\winsat.exe"